   "x": 40,
   "y": 316,
   "width": 1573.08,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Containment picks the narrowest action that stops the exposed path without erasing root-cause evidence. A corrective change isn't done on one successful save: the old credential or route has to fail after the new one works before the incident closes.",
